e sky, our results do not support the evidence\nfor spatial $\\alpha$ variation, especially when combined with the 21 other\nrecent measurements which were corrected for, or resistant to, long-range\ndistortions. Our spectra and absorption profile fits are publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jul 2017 18:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
