ogy in large enough degrees is that of the product of the algebras on\nthe diagonal.\n  As a by-product, we obtain some families of bound quiver algebras which are\nof infinite global dimension, and have Hochschild cohomology zero in large\nenough degrees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 08:45:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2018 16:20:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-02"}
