y grains. The 3-$\\mu$m absorption band from water ice is not\ndetected in the spectra acquired during the outbursts, whereas signatures of\norganic compounds near 3.4 $\\mu$m are observed in emission. The H$_2$O\n2.7-$\\mu$m and CO$_2$ 4.3-$\\mu$m vibrational bands do not show any enhancement\nduring the outbursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 09:06:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-08"}
