ties for advanced memristive memory and computing\narchitectures, e.g., in-memory computing and neuromorphics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 14:51:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 12:27:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-19"}
